details.text: Platform interface logic.
Global interconnect for 13 global loads and 5 global stores. Reduce number of global loads and stores to simplify global interconnect.
See %L for more information

Load uses a Burst-coalesced cached LSU.  Load with a private 64 kilobit cache. Cache is not shared with any other load. It is flushed on kernel start. Use Dynamic Profiler to verify cache effectiveness. Other kernels should not be updating the data in global memory while this kernel is using it. Cache is created when memory access pattern is data-dependent or appears to be repetitive. Simplify access pattern or mark pointer as 'volatile' to disable generation of this cache.
Load uses a Burst-coalesced non-aligned LSU.  Use Dynamic Profiler to determine performance impact of this LSU.
